        ": إنّ ذنوب المؤمنين مغفورة لهم فليعمل المؤمن لما يستأنف، أما إنّها ليست إلاّ لأهل الايمان."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.badr-shahin": [
          "(The same previous series of relaters)… from al-Hasan in Mahboub from al-Alaa from Mohammed bin Muslim that Abu Ja’far (a) said: The sins of the believers are already forgiven. Hence, a believer should put a new start. This is surely granted for the people of faith exclusively."
        ]
